动浏览器访问其<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://pikmin-finder.nintendo.net/">网站</a>，然后开始在手机上捕捉皮克敏。 You can also scan the QR code that shows up on the website when you open it on a desktop browser.</p> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/nintendos-new-mobile-game-lets-you-pluck-pikmin-on-your-browser-064423362.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/nintendos-new-mobile-game-lets-you-pluck-pikmin-on-your-browser-064423362.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> ce7445db-6d28-444a-8b98-b1d51cdc7302</guid><dc:creator> Mariella Moon</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher> Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Tue, 05 Sep 2023 06:44:23 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1693896245</ingested><modified> 2023-09-05T06:44:09+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Utility Industry]]></category><category><![CDATA[Personal Finance - Career & Education]]></category><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Handheld & Connected Devices]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Mariella Moon]]></category><media:content height="720" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/83803990-4bb0-11ee-bf6d-199b1c5976db" width="1280"><media:keywords> headline </media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="720" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/8